KEY CATEGORY INSIGHTS:
- Tables: Highest market share (23.8%) and best volume performance (81.1 sales per product)
- Decor: Highest revenue per unit sold ($138.96) indicating premium positioning
- Bedroom: Largest product count (479 products) but lower sales velocity
- Office: Good balance of volume and revenue generation
- Storage: Lowest revenue per product, potential for optimization

