====================================================================
SUMMARY INSIGHTS & RECOMMENDATIONS
====================================================================

SALES PERFORMANCE:
- 77.4% of products have low to no sales (0-10 units)
- Top 10 products generate significant revenue concentration
- High revenue loss (55.7%) due to discounting strategy

CATEGORY PERFORMANCE:
- Tables and Bedroom categories dominate market (43.6% combined share)
- Significant variation in revenue per unit across categories
- Office and Storage categories show good volume potential

SEGMENT INSIGHTS:
- Segment 2 (Mid-Range Popular) represents the largest volume (71.9% of products)
- Budget Best-Sellers segment shows exceptional performance potential
- Premium segment needs attention for improved conversion

KEY STRATEGIC PRIORITIES:
1. Focus on Tables category expansion (highest performer)
2. Scale Budget Best-Sellers segment (critical priority)
3. Address non-performing products (22.6% zero sales)
4. Optimize discount strategy to reduce revenue loss
5. Improve Premium segment visibility and conversion

